02:09:43,560 --> 02:09:45,960
- That's not true.
- Well, I can't.

1920
02:09:47,560 --> 02:09:50,120
And I want you to know, Lisa,

1921
02:09:50,199 --> 02:09:53,000
I'm very, very proud of you for
pursuing this the way that you have.

1922
