1933
02:10:27,239 --> 02:10:29,800
- All right.
- We didn't need a big conference about it.

1934
02:10:29,880 --> 02:10:31,200
No, it's not a big conference.

1935
02:10:31,279 --> 02:10:34,640
I just wanted to know
what was going on.

1936
02:10:36,000 --> 02:10:38,120
And I wanted to meet you, Emily.

1937
02:10:39,119 --> 02:10:40,840
I know it's a little awkward.

1938
