Because it's your intention
to make me start crying!

1957
02:11:35,960 --> 02:11:37,240
No, it's not.

1958
02:11:37,880 --> 02:11:39,280
You want to move to LA, move to LA.

1959
02:11:39,359 --> 02:11:41,680
Why can't this even be mentioned
without you taking it personally?

1960
02:11:41,760 --> 02:11:43,920
I'm just introducing a possibility!

1961
02:11:44,000 --> 02:11:46,800
Here's a possibility, that you can
make your own fucking dinner!

1962
02:11:46,880 --> 02:11:48,760
Here's a possibility, that you can
do whatever you want to do...

1963
02:11:48,840 --> 02:11:50,040
Jesus Christ! What is with you?

1964
02:11:50,119 --> 02:11:51,520
I don't care anymore,
you heartless little fucking bitch!

1965
02:11:51,600 --> 02:11:53,080
Fine! Keep it up! This really
makes me want to stay here!

1966
02:11:53,159 --> 02:11:55,080
You think you're so fucking perfect?

1967
02:11:55,399 --> 02:11:56,440
No!

1968
02:11:59,840 --> 02:12:01,680
- Nice one.
