02:41:46,799 --> 02:41:48,000
I was gonna say,

2452
02:41:48,079 --> 02:41:50,080
I know there was a concern
after our last call

2453
02:41:50,159 --> 02:41:52,200
that we were jumping
the gun a little bit.

