02:42:10,319 --> 02:42:13,080
Hey, $350,000, that's
nothing to sneeze at.

2463
02:42:13,159 --> 02:42:14,880
<i>Let me just... I just want
to introduce the thought...</i>

2464
02:42:14,959 --> 02:42:17,160
<i>- Can you all hear me?
- Yes!</i>

2465
02:42:17,239 --> 02:42:19,120
<i>Was that everybody? Okay.</i>

2466
02:42:19,200 --> 02:42:20,840
<i>Emily? What do you think?</i>

2467
02:42:22,239 --> 02:42:24,120
