like we should do it.

2468
02:42:24,239 --> 02:42:25,800
<i>- But I'd like to be...
- Okay. If that's the vote.</i>

2469
02:42:25,879 --> 02:42:29,080
<i>Unless you think there's something to
be gained from holding out for more.</i>

2470
02:42:29,159 --> 02:42:30,840
