2471
02:42:30,920 --> 02:42:32,360
<i>Robbie, what do you think?</i>

2472
02:42:37,600 --> 02:42:38,920
<i>- Sold!
- Sold!</i>

2473
02:42:39,000 --> 02:42:40,280
Okay.

2474
02:42:40,520 --> 02:42:43,560
Now, the only downside
to this as it stands,

2475
02:42:44,639 --> 02:42:46,480
and the reason I asked
Lisa and Emily to be here

