may not know, Lisa,

2491
02:43:24,559 --> 02:43:27,160
that they're currently involved in a
very tricky labor dispute right now.

2492
02:43:27,239 --> 02:43:30,080
Yeah, we know all about that!
Just tell them to forget it.

2493
02:43:30,159 --> 02:43:32,240
- I know that's your reaction...
- It's the only reason we're here.

2494
02:43:32,360 --> 02:43:35,040
<i>- Can I jump in here? Russel?
- It's really not your decision.</i>

2495
02:43:35,120 --> 02:43:36,520
<i>- It's Emily's decision.
- Hello?</i>

2496
02:43:36,600 --> 02:43:37,880
- No.
- It's not?

2497
02:43:37,959 --> 02:43:40,080
