2518
02:44:22,440 --> 02:44:24,440
<i>Well, I'm sorry, but I
have a responsibility</i>

2519
02:44:24,520 --> 02:44:27,800
<i>to Monica, and I take that
responsibility very seriously.</i>

2520
02:44:27,879 --> 02:44:30,280
<i>And rather than being abused
over the telephone and cursed at</i>

