2536
02:45:12,559 --> 02:45:16,520
<i>and to my mind is a positive result of
all this tragedy, and not just negative.</i>

2537
02:45:16,600 --> 02:45:19,440
<i>Not just getting someone fired for one
mistake, no matter how bad it was.</i>

2538
02:45:19,520 --> 02:45:20,920
Shove it up your ass!

2539
02:45:21,000 --> 02:45:22,040
Lisa!

2540
02:45:22,120 --> 02:45:25,080
